\h 1 Vakolinto
\toc2 1 Vakolinto
\toc1 Ibalula ya wutasi iya Pawulo kwa Vakolinto
\mt2 Ibalula ya wutasi iya Pawulo kwa
\mt1 Vakolinto
\imt Imola yina yilongola
\ip Umwanandeje uPawulo wáyandikhaga ibalula iyi kwa vahuvililaaji ava ku lijumbi lya Kolinto. Ilijumbi ilyo, likhandi lijumbi likhome mu nyi ya Akaya ku Wuyunaani, khanji likhandi limanyikha mandu mu nyi yoona iya Wuyunaani. UPawulo wákhomaga mu lijumbi ilyo umwakha gumo na kishila (\xt Nsengo sa Vanandeje 18:1-18\xt*). Avaanu vinshi vamuhuvililaga uYeesu, leelo uPawulo wáganaga kiwuukha mu Kolinto, avahuvililaaji va Yeesu vayansa kibagunkhana mu lihuuvi. Ndeeno, uPawulo wáyandikhaga ibalula iyi kivatanga avahuvililaaji vala, kiija vasingamale wunofu mu lihuuvi.
\ip Mu balula iyi, itaviilila uwuvi wa kibagunkhana avahuvililaaji na kikhaanania ulwa lihuuvi mu shipuga sha vahuvililaaji va Yeesu. Itaviilila shina uNumbula uMunofu ikitupeela ifipeelwa finshi. Itaviilila mandu ulugano luna lukitutanga kimufuunya uNguluvi na kiiva ni njendo inofu mu lihuuvi. Khanji ikivakumbusa kiija, uKilisito wáfyukhaga kihuma kwa vina vafwile, ndeeno timeenye kiija akhayinsa kitufyusa, na yuuse tive wuumi khanji.
\tr \th1 Umulyango\th2 Gina gakwali mu litaafili ili
\tr \tc1 1:1-9\tc2 UPawulo ikivahunjila aVakolinto na kimuhonjesa uNguluvi kwa kiiva ya veene
